Class CamelCompositeProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.james.mailetcontainer.lib.AbstractStateCompositeProcessor
      • org.apache.james.mailetcontainer.impl.camel.CamelCompositeProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.camel.CamelContextAware, Configurable, LogEnabled, MailProcessor

    public class CamelCompositeProcessor
extends AbstractStateCompositeProcessor
implements org.apache.camel.CamelContextAware
    Build up the Camel Routes by parsing the mailetcontainer.xml configuration file. It also offer the AbstractStateCompositeProcessor implementation which allow to inject Mail into the routes.
